                        </th>
                        <th style="writing-mode: vertical-rl; transform: rotate(180deg); min-width:45px;">
                            Nivel de riesgo
                        </th>
                        <th style="writing-mode: vertical-rl; transform: rotate(180deg); min-width:45px;">
